Rongga dada awak dah kosong.

23:42.350 --> 23:43.440
Semuanya

23:44.570 --> 23:46.530
sangat selamat,

23:48.850 --> 23:50.360
sangat tenang,

23:53.100 --> 23:53.970
sangat

23:55.210 --> 23:56.300
aman.

24:09.160 --> 24:10.690
Mari kita cuba sekali lagi.

24:11.520 --> 24:12.320
Relaks.

24:14.690 --> 24:16.620
Tarik nafas dalam-dalam.

24:18.030 --> 24:19.630
Secara perlahan-lahannya,

24:21.130 --> 24:22.610
