27:32.220 --> 27:32.640
Berhenti!

27:32.640 --> 27:33.550
Jangan sentuh saya!

27:33.550 --> 27:34.180
Berhenti!

27:34.200 --> 27:34.930
Jangan!

27:36.560 --> 27:38.420
